{"tid":145972,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家屌醒我呢隻臭雞","createTime":"2017-03-06T16:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T07:58:00.000Z","uid":26243,"like":10,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f17adbabc944484659f8a4ad080cc12ba158c957","tid":145972,"uid":26243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左都一段時間<br />\n初初都覺得好開心好幸福<br />\n但唔知係一齊耐左定點<br />\n我覺得男朋友好似成日都唔想理我唔想掂我<br />\n冇左以前岩岩一齊個種好熱戀嘅感覺<br />\n我覺得好唔開心 好想翻翻去以前<br />\n好想佢一見到我就對我好熱情<br />\n唔想好似而家咁 變到好老夫老妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有日貪得意去識左個男仔<br />\n個男仔比到我好想要嘅個種熱戀感覺我<br />\n佢對我好好 雖然我唔知佢係想呃閪屌定點<br />\n但同佢一齊 我覺得好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己好矛盾 我唔知自己想點<br />\n我出去搵第二個嘅時候係好開心好滿足<br />\n一完左就好頹廢<br />\n見男朋友時不斷諗翻個個男仔 個心好唔舒服<br />\n唉 大家盡情屌醒我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f65a72109eb98c26f711e0245e6d12f382508c6","tid":145972,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"就算俾你散左同條新仔一齊，過左一段時間咪又係咁，到最後都係無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee08c57b37ef362e1afce8895804725c91bdeb2","tid":145972,"uid":26243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算俾你散左同條新仔一齊，過左一段時間咪又係咁，到最後都係無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪拍拖耐左就一定會變成咁？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我真係愛我男朋友架但我真係好似已經搵唔翻個種熱戀嘅感覺 好辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7436b5eb922a2eca6bf3e64a1e32bb99ff2399","tid":145972,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply