/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都冇諗過自己竟然會背叛男朋友<br />\n我都以為自己會同男朋友穩穩定定一直落去<br />\n我係咪應該要改自己心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊得耐一定會係咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8170f66433551538e0c78e6044a571126cd1b9b7","tid":145972,"uid":83741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"拍足廿年，廿年都熱戀咩？出軌都仲咁多理由，放過你男朋友啦"},{"pid":"a2d07e6e93e1db255b508139d436bbbf7b6a2dcc","tid":145972,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"我唔會怪樓主 我明白點解女人會出軌<br />\n女人出軌好多時唔係因為新鮮感感 而係覺得另一半唔在乎 唔再咁愛自己 一傷心就在外搵其他人安慰<br />\n<br />\n樓主 我唔會怪你<br />\n如果你條仔經已對你唔好 唔再愛你 你有所有理由搵過第二個<br />\n<br />\n另外 老夫老妻唔等於感情淡如水 你個情況到底係真係老夫老妻定係雞肋 你自己間自己喇"},{"pid":"32ed0d35a347632e9950e39529ec5a4ae077ad14","tid":145972,"uid":13286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:56:49.000Z","msg":"比著我都唔開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女友做哂主動都唔理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417ac36f9eb0c483477155ae4a1c63e3e737e49d","tid":145972,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"點解呢個年代咁撚多你呢d不忠既女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   成日比帽仔帶   不如你死左佢算啦 唔好留係到害鳩人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4e613f8a4c68cb0954652afe69e37f513aa297","tid":145972,"uid":26243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:43:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔會怪樓主 我明白點解女人會出軌<br />\n女人出軌好多時唔係因為新鮮感感 而係覺得另一半唔在乎 唔再咁愛自己 一傷心就在外搵其他人安慰<br />\n<br />\n樓主 我唔會怪你<br />\n如果你條仔經已對你唔好 唔再愛你 你有所有理由搵過第二個<br />\n<br />\n另外 老夫老妻唔等於感情淡如水 你個情況到底係真係老夫老妻定係雞肋 你自己間自己喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都覺得自己係佢心目中已經唔係咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..... 好想要翻個種比人放第一位 捧係手心錫嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949eb0ca1e920b542ffcecd07b5c9421f9ddc4ab","tid":145972,"uid":26243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解呢個年代咁撚多你呢d不忠既女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   成日比帽仔帶   不如你死左佢算啦 唔好留係到害鳩人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係我唔岩我應該死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a60e2cb4d06aef38d9c675e3c0ada1983a47b04","tid":145972,"uid":13277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:50:05.000Z","msg":"隔離撚香D"},{"pid":"1228d91848f0ce18c8a31e533d9b026ba6a6bd7a","tid":145972,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放過你男朋友啦"},{"pid":"b2a0e4646f622386d2947b33785d48831023e03f","tid":145972,"uid":53522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:53:44.000Z","msg":"約個時間 房錢我出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f3eb71b07392b94b702a2ab3e